Analyze Your Data

Preserve and Share CRM Analytics Dashboard Views in a Collection

Create dashboard views with selected filters and options then add them to your collections to share a specific view of the dashboard with others.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To manage a collection: 
Use CRM Analytics
Open a dashboard
Make selections or change dashboard filters to get the view of the data you want
Click the Add to Collection button
Select one or more collections or click Create Collection to start a new one
Click Save

Updates to the dashboard definition, such as changes to the layout, widget, or query, are reflected in the dashboard view with exception of initial filter selections and default landing page updates.

Get Started Using CRM Analytics
title: Preserve and Share CRM Analytics Dashboard Views
